							<v8:lang>en</v8:lang>
							<v8:content>Insured in the system of a person of compulsory pension insurance of the number of foreign citizens or stateless persons, temporarily residing in the territory of the Russian Federation, as well as temporarily staying on the territory of the Russian Federation, foreign citizens or stateless persons who have been granted temporary asylum in accordance with the Federal Law of 19 February 1993 № 4528-1 «on refugees" on the benefits and rewards that accrued premiums organizations that have received the status of participants of the project osusches Applicants' research, development and commercialization of the results in accordance with the Federal Law of 28.09.2010 number 244-FZ "On the Innovation Center" Skolkovo "</v8:content>
